'''CCL1'''（{{lang-en|Chemokine (C-C motif) ligand 1}}）是一小分子的[[细胞因子|细胞因子]]属于CC[[趋化因子|趋化因子]]家族，是由活化的[[T细胞|T细胞]]分泌的[[糖蛋白|糖蛋白]]<ref name=miller>Miller MD, Krangel MS. The human cytokine I-309 is a monocyte chemoattractant. Proc Natl Acad Sci U S A. 1992 Apr 1;89(7):2950-4.</ref>。CCL1与细胞表面的趋化因子受体[[CCR8|CCR8]]结合<ref>Roos RS, Loetscher M, Legler DF, Clark-Lewis I, Baggiolini M, Moser B. Identification of CCR8, the receptor for the human CC chemokine I-309. J Biol Chem. 1997 Jul 11;272(28):17251-4.</ref>。CCL1对[[单核细胞|单核细胞]]，[[自然杀伤细胞|自然杀伤细胞]]，未成熟的[[B细胞|B细胞]]和[[树突状细胞|树突状细胞]]有细胞趋化作用<ref name=miller>Miller MD, Krangel MS. The human cytokine I-309 is a monocyte chemoattractant. Proc Natl Acad Sci U S A. 1992 Apr 1;89(7):2950-4.</ref>。人类的CCL1[[基因|基因]]与许多CC趋化因子的基因相邻聚集在第17染色体上<ref>Miller MD, Wilson SD, Dorf ME, Seuanez HN, O'Brien SJ, Krangel MS. Sequence and chromosomal location of the I-309 gene. Relationship to genes encoding a family of inflammatory cytokines. J Immunol. 1990 Oct 15;145(8):2737-44.</ref>.

